  "cs": "<h2>Jawa OZ-350 (1950) – Československá legenda</h2><p>Jawa OZ-350 je kultovní československý motocykl z dílny Závodů 9. května v Praze. Tento dvoutaktní stroj s objemem 350 ccm představuje zlatou éru československého motorismu. Model se vyznačuje robustní konstrukcí, jednoduchou údržbou a bezpečnou jízdou na dlouhé vzdálenosti.</p><h3>Technické specifikace:</h3><table style='border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%; margin: 15px 0;'><tr style='border-bottom: 2px solid #333;'><th style='text-align: left; padding: 8px; border-right: 1px solid #ccc;'>Vlastnost</th><th style='text-align: left; padding: 8px;'>Hodnota</th></tr><tr style='border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;'><td style='padding: 8px; border-right: 1px solid #ccc;'><strong>Druh vozidla</strong></td><td style='padding: 8px;'>Motocykl</td></tr><tr style='border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;'><td style='padding: 8px; border-right: 1px solid #ccc;'><strong>Značka a typ</strong></td><td style='padding: 8px;'>Jawa OZ-350</td></tr><tr style='border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;'><td style='padding: 8px; border-right: 1px solid #ccc;'><strong>Výrobce</strong></td><td style='padding: 8px;'>Závody 9. května, Praha</td></tr><tr style='border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;'><td style='padding: 8px; border-right: 1px solid #ccc;'><strong>Rok výroby</strong></td><td style='padding: 8px;'>1950</td></tr><tr style='border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;'><td style='padding: 8px; border-right: 1px solid #ccc;'><strong>Objem motoru</strong></td><td style='padding: 8px;'>344 cm³ (350 ccm)</td></tr><tr style='border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;'><td style='padding: 8px; border-right: 1px solid #ccc;'><strong>Typ motoru</strong></td><td style='padding: 8px;'>Dvoutaktní, 2 válce, vzduchově chlazen</td></tr><tr style='border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;'><td style='padding: 8px; border-right: 1px solid #ccc;'><strong>Vrtání / Zdvih</strong></td><td style='padding: 8px;'>58 mm / 65 mm</td></tr><tr style='border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;'><td style='padding: 8px; border-right: 1px solid #ccc;'><strong>Maximální výkon</strong></td><td style='padding: 8px;'>16 k.s. (asi 47 500 ot./min)</td></tr><tr style='border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;'><td style='padding: 8px; border-right: 1px solid #ccc;'><strong>Pohonné palivo</strong></td><td style='padding: 8px;'>Benzín se směsí</td></tr><tr style='border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;'><td style='padding: 8px; border-right: 1px solid #ccc;'><strong>Počet míst</strong></td><td style='padding: 8px;'>2 (1 k sezení, 1 k stání)</td></tr><tr style='border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;'><td style='padding: 8px; border-right: 1px solid #ccc;'><strong>Délka</strong></td><td style='padding: 8px;'>1 980 mm</td></tr><tr style='border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;'><td style='padding: 8px; border-right: 1px solid #ccc;'><strong>Šířka</strong></td><td style='padding: 8px;'>670 mm</td></tr><tr style='border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;'><td style='padding: 8px; border-right: 1px solid #ccc;'><strong>Výška</strong></td><td style='padding: 8px;'>1 025 mm</td></tr><tr style='border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;'><td style='padding: 8px; border-right: 1px solid #ccc;'><strong>Rozvor kol</strong></td><td style='padding: 8px;'>1 318 mm</td></tr><tr style='border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;'><td style='padding: 8px; border-right: 1px solid #ccc;'><strong>Počet kol</strong></td><td style='padding: 8px;'>2 (drátenné kolo)</td></tr><tr style='border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;'><td style='padding: 8px; border-right: 1px solid #ccc;'><strong>Pneumatiky</strong></td><td style='padding: 8px;'>3.25 - 16 (přední i zadní)</td></tr><tr style='border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;'><td style='padding: 8px; border-right: 1px solid #ccc;'><strong>Ráfky</strong></td><td style='padding: 8px;'>1.85 x 16 (přední i zadní)</td></tr><tr style='border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;'><td style='padding: 8px; border-right: 1px solid #ccc;'><strong>Zvláštnění výbava</strong></td><td style='padding: 8px;'>Navijáka, plachta, oblouky a příslušenství</td></tr><tr style='border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;'><td style='padding: 8px; border-right: 1px solid #ccc;'><strong>Váhy - Pohotovostní váha</strong></td><td style='padding: 8px;'>152 kg</td></tr><tr style='border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;'><td style='padding: 8px; border-right: 1px solid #ccc;'><strong>Váhy - Užitečné zatížení</strong></td><td style='padding: 8px;'>105 kg</td></tr><tr style='border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;'><td style='padding: 8px; border-right: 1px solid #ccc;'><strong>Váhy - Celková váha</strong></td><td style='padding: 8px;'>160 kg</td></tr><tr style='border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;'><td style='padding: 8px; border-right: 1px solid #ccc;'><strong>Váhy náprav - Přední náprava</strong></td><td style='padding: 8px;'>cca 80 kg</td></tr><tr style='border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;'><td style='padding: 8px; border-right: 1px solid #ccc;'><strong>Váhy náprav - Zadní náprava</strong></td><td style='padding: 8px;'>207 kg</td></tr><tr style='border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;'><td style='padding: 8px; border-right: 1px solid #ccc;'><strong>Brzdy</strong></td><td style='padding: 8px;'>Mechanické celistvé</td></tr><tr style='border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;'><td style='padding: 8px; border-right: 1px solid #ccc;'><strong>Nejvyšší rychlost</strong></td><td style='padding: 8px;'>120 km/h</td></tr><tr style='border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;'><td style='padding: 8px; border-right: 1px solid #ccc;'><strong>Základní spotřeba paliva (50 km/h)</strong></td><td style='padding: 8px;'>6 l na 100 km</td></tr></table><p>Jawa OZ-350 zůstává věrným svědkem československé motoristické tradice a je velmi vyhledávanou sběratelskou položkou. Technický průkaz vydán ministerstvem dopravy dne 10.9.1955.</p>",
  "en": "<h2>Jawa OZ-350 (1950) – Czechoslovak Legend</h2><p>The Jawa OZ-350 is a cult Czechoslovak motorcycle from the workshops of the May 9 Works in Prague. This two-stroke machine with a displacement of 350 cc represents the golden age of Czechoslovak motorcycling. The model is characterized by robust construction, simple maintenance, and safe long-distance riding.</p><h3>Technical Specifications:</h3><table style='border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%; margin: 15px 0;'><tr style='border-bottom: 2px solid #333;'><th style='text-align: left; padding: 8px; border-right: 1px solid #ccc;'>Property</th><th style='text-align: left; padding: 8px;'>Value</th></tr><tr style='border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;'><td style='padding: 8px; border-right: 1px solid #ccc;'><strong>Vehicle Type</strong></td><td style='padding: 8px;'>Motorcycle</td></tr><tr style='border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;'><td style='padding: 8px; border-right: 1px solid #ccc;'><strong>Make and Model</strong></td><td style='padding: 8px;'>Jawa OZ-350</td></tr><tr style='border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;'><td style='padding: 8px; border-right: 1px solid #ccc;'><strong>Manufacturer</strong></td><td style='padding: 8px;'>May 9 Works, Prague</td></tr><tr style='border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;'><td style='padding: 8px; border-right: 1px solid #ccc;'><strong>Year of Manufacture</strong></td><td style='padding: 8px;'>1950</td></tr><tr style='border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;'><td style='padding: 8px; border-right: 1px solid #ccc;'><strong>Engine Displacement</strong></td><td style='padding: 8px;'>344 cm³ (350 cc)</td></tr><tr style='border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;'><td style='padding: 8px; border-right: 1px solid #ccc;'><strong>Engine Type</strong></td><td style='padding: 8px;'>Two-stroke, 2 cylinders, air-cooled</td></tr><tr style='border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;'><td style='padding: 8px; border-right: 1px solid #ccc;'><strong>Bore / Stroke</strong></td><td style='padding: 8px;'>58 mm / 65 mm</td></tr><tr style='border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;'><td style='padding: 8px; border-right: 1px solid #ccc;'><strong>Maximum Power</strong></td><td style='padding: 8px;'>16 hp (approx. 47,500 rpm)</td></tr><tr style='border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;'><td style='padding: 8px; border-right: 1px solid #ccc;'><strong>Fuel Type</strong></td><td style='padding: 8px;'>Petrol with oil mix</td></tr><tr style='border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;'><td style='padding: 8px; border-right: 1px solid #ccc;'><strong>Number of Seats</strong></td><td style='padding: 8px;'>2 (1 sitting, 1 standing)</td></tr><tr style='border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;'><td style='padding: 8px; border-right: 1px solid #ccc;'><strong>Length</strong></td><td style='padding: 8px;'>1,980 mm</td></tr><tr style='border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;'><td style='padding: 8px; border-right: 1px solid #ccc;'><strong>Width</strong></td><td style='padding: 8px;'>670 mm</td></tr><tr style='border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;'><td style='padding: 8px; border-right: 1px solid #ccc;'><strong>Height</strong></td><td style='padding: 8px;'>1,025 mm</td></tr><tr style='border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;'><td style='padding: 8px; border-right: 1px solid #ccc;'><strong>Wheelbase</strong></td><td style='padding: 8px;'>1,318 mm</td></tr><tr style='border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;'><td style='padding: 8px; border-right: 1px solid #ccc;'><strong>Number of Wheels</strong></td><td style='padding: 8px;'>2 (wire wheels)</td></tr><tr style='border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;'><td style='padding: 8px; border-right: 1px solid #ccc;'><strong>Tires</strong></td><td style='padding: 8px;'>3.25 - 16 (front and rear)</td></tr><tr style='border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;'><td style='padding: 8px; border-right: 1px solid #ccc;'><strong>Rims</strong></td><td style='padding: 8px;'>1.85 x 16 (front and rear)</td></tr><tr style='border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;'><td style='padding: 8px; border-right: 1px solid #ccc;'><strong>Special Equipment</strong></td><td style='padding: 8px;'>Winch, tarpaulin, bows and accessories</td></tr><tr style='border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;'><td style='padding: 8px; border-right: 1px solid #ccc;'><strong>Weight - Curb Weight</strong></td><td style='padding: 8px;'>152 kg</td></tr><tr style='border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;'><td style='padding: 8px; border-right: 1px solid #ccc;'><strong>Weight - Useful Load</strong></td><td style='padding: 8px;'>105 kg</td></tr><tr style='border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;'><td style='padding: 8px; border-right: 1px solid #ccc;'><strong>Weight - Total Weight</strong></td><td style='padding: 8px;'>160 kg</td></tr><tr style='border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;'><td style='padding: 8px; border-right: 1px solid #ccc;'><strong>Axle Weights - Front Axle</strong></td><td style='padding: 8px;'>approx. 80 kg</td></tr><tr style='border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;'><td style='padding: 8px; border-right: 1px solid #ccc;'><strong>Axle Weights - Rear Axle</strong></td><td style='padding: 8px;'>207 kg</td></tr><tr style='border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;'><td style='padding: 8px; border-right: 1px solid #ccc;'><strong>Brakes</strong></td><td style='padding: 8px;'>Mechanical integral</td></tr><tr style='border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;'><td style='padding: 8px; border-right: 1px solid #ccc;'><strong>Maximum Speed</strong></td><td style='padding: 8px;'>120 km/h</td></tr><tr style='border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;'><td style='padding: 8px; border-right: 1px solid #ccc;'><strong>Basic Fuel Consumption (50 km/h)</strong></td><td style='padding: 8px;'>6 l per 100 km</td></tr></table><p>The Jawa OZ-350 remains a faithful witness to Czechoslovak motorcycle tradition and is a highly sought-after collectible item. Technical certificate issued by the Ministry of Transport on September 10, 1955.</p>"
